Dear Hiring Manager,

Im a passionate and self-taught Full Stack Developer skilled in the MEAN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, Angular, Node.js) with a strong enthusiasm for building efficient, scalable, and user-friendly web applications.

Over the past year, Ive dedicated myself to mastering full stack development through project-based learning and real-world challenges. Ive built and deployed applications involving RESTful APIs, responsive UI components, and database integrations  all from scratch. Each project taught me not just how to write better code, but how to think like a problem solver, work in a structured environment, and prioritize user experience and performance.

My strengths include:

Designing clean and modular architecture using Angular and Node.js.

Creating secure, high-performance APIs using Express.js and MongoDB.

Developing responsive interfaces with Angular and Material Design.

Deploying applications on cloud platforms and using Git/GitHub for version control.

Im continuously exploring new tools and best practices, from JWT authentication to Angular state management, and I enjoy contributing to collaborative projects. As a fresher, I bring a fresh perspective, strong learning agility, and hunger to grow in a fast-paced, real-world environment.

I am now seeking a role where I can apply my MEAN stack skills, collaborate with like-minded developers, and continue to evolve as a professional. I would be grateful for an opportunity to contribute and grow as part of a dynamic development team.

Thank you for your time and consideration. I invite you to explore my portfolio to see the kind of work I do. I look forward to the opportunity to bring my skills and energy to your team.

Warm regards,
Arunabha Das
